{Speech 2}{}{Passing by a small village in the wasteland, you see a crowd of people trying to burn a woman at the stake, accompanying it all with shouts of: "We got the witch! A witch! A witch!". Your actions:}
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{Wait for the situation to resolve itself, and then check whether the witch has anything valuable among her belongings...}
{Speech 2 Answer 4}{}{You try to make sense of the situation, suggesting to reason logically and refrain from needless violence - and in the end, coming to the conclusion that: If the witch weighs the same as a duck, then she is made of wood...}
{Speech 2 Answer 3}{}{[More]}
{Speech 3}{}{Passing by a small village in the wasteland, you see a crowd of people trying to burn a woman at the stake, accompanying it all with shouts of: "We got the witch! A witch! A witch!". Your actions:}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit}{}{In 5 seconds you assess the situation, hear out your inner voice as the prosecution, single-handedly pass sentence on the participants of the conflict, and start killing people, comforting yourself with the thought of justice prevailing…}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit*}{}{Pray to the heavens that the world is so meager and limited that people are forced to merely burn and shoot other people, without alternatives such as hanging or drowning.}
{Speech 3 Answer 2}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit**}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 4}{}{You meet a young girl with a brahmin in the wasteland. It seems she's lost. Your actions:}
{Speech 4 Answer Exit}{}{Ask whether she has a spare gun, while also inquiring where to find ammo, where the bank is in Klamath, and whether she has 100 coins?}
{Speech 4 Answer 6}{}{Ask what happened to her and try to escort her home despite the stench from the brahmin. Another dangerous and heroic rescue on your glorious path.}
{Speech 4 Answer 5}{}{[More]}
{Speech 5}{}{You meet a young girl with a brahmin in the wasteland. It seems she's lost. Your actions:}
{Speech 5 Answer Exit}{}{Being @sex@|sure|sure|, that you recently saw this brahmin together with bandits, you decide it's an ambush, and execute both, shouting that they won't fool you and that you'll cleanse the wasteland of carrion.}
{Speech 5 Answer Exit*}{}{Silently walk on, paying no attention to the girl, pondering the fact that you've never seen little brahmin calves and how the hell they even breed here at all.}
{Speech 5 Answer 4}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 5 Answer Exit**}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 6}{}{Into how many parts do you usually dismember corpses?}
{Speech 6 Answer 8}{}{What???}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{Six, of course, how else could it be? Although for children you don't have to chop off the head.}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit*}{}{That's @sex@|women's|men's| work! @sex@|A real man should only eat the heart of a slain enemy, after first tearing it out of the chest!|We kill with special cruelty - they dismember|}
{Speech 6 Answer 7}{}{[More]}
{Speech 7}{}{Into how many parts do you usually dismember corpses?}
{Speech 7 Answer Exit}{}{Why dismember?! I usually just cut off the fingers to take the rings.}
