{Speech 7 Answer Exit*}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 8}{}{After a shootout in the city you notice a man running straight toward one of the corpses. Your actions:}
{Speech 8 Answer Exit}{}{Quickly get your bearings and try to reach the corpse first, so that all the loot goes to you.}
{Speech 8 Answer 10}{}{Wait to see how the situation develops, maybe this man is just running past on his own business in the city, and his route happens to cross the spot where the corpse lies.}
{Speech 8 Answer 9}{}{[More]}
{Speech 9}{}{After a shootout in the city you notice a man running straight toward one of the corpses. Your actions:}
{Speech 9 Answer Exit}{}{Kill him on the spot, it's obvious he's a vile looter.}
{Speech 9 Answer Exit*}{}{Kill him on the spot, since you came to the city to kill.}
{Speech 9 Answer 8}{}{[Back]}
