{Speech 10}{}{Sitting in a bar, you happened to overhear a conversation about how a place is about to open where people involved in mass murders, robberies and rapes will live and rest. Your actions:}
{Speech 10 Answer Exit}{}{Decide that you absolutely must visit this place, since all your friends will be there.}
{Speech 10 Answer Exit*}{}{Decide that you shouldn't go in there… or you'll get raped, robbed and killed again…}
